Get to know your customer really, really well.

And that is hard. For any size business. It‚Äôs as hard as it is vitally important, because everything you do, from developing your product, to marketing your product, to creating a brand that drives customers to you ‚Äì it all starts here.

To do that, you have to define who, exactly, you need to talk to.

And that starts by developing a hypothesis.

